sentences.english: No words can express the grandeur of that parade.

sentences.english: Trooping the Colour is a ceremony to honour Queen Elizabeth's official birthday. The Queen celebrates her 90th birthday this year.

sentences.english: To complete the military ceremony, 60 planes will fly past.
